subject: ATTENTIONBENEFICIARY
body:
ATTENTIONBENEFICIARY
I received your email The world bank dipomatic official that will be
arriving in your country with your sealed consignment that contain
your contract payment of US$28.5 MILLION dollar to be delivered to you
once he arrive in your country origin. Reconfirm back to me your full
address, occupation your private cell phone number your copy of
international passport, to enable me forward it to the world bank
diplomatic official in swizzerland that will be arriving in your
country by monday next week 29th of September 2023
You'll be required to pay for your diplomatic clearance fee and
handling charges of US6,500 dollar once he arrive in your country he
will contact you for clearing of your sealed consignmrnt that
contained your contract cash payment sealed in a consignment.
MY REGARDS TO YOUR FAMILY
Dr.MELE KYARI
GROUP MANAGING Contract Bill Payment
Eastern Gas Gathering System
(EGGS).N.N.P.C

subject: Re:   ATTENTIONBENEFICIARY
body:
Dear Mr. Kyari,

Thank you for your email. I am excited to hear about the arrival of the diplomatic official with my contract payment. However, I would like to clarify a few things before we proceed.

Firstly, could you please provide more details about this contract? It would be helpful to understand the nature of this contract and why I am receiving such a significant amount.

Secondly, regarding the diplomatic clearance fee and handling charges, could you please provide more information on how these fees are calculated and why they are necessary?

Lastly, I would appreciate it if you could confirm the exact date of arrival of the diplomatic official in my country.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Tina
